    "Other models like KNN, SVM, and MLP yielded a latency of about 0.01 s but with low test accuracy.",
    "Identifying the most appropriate model for addressing a given problem necessitates thorough consideration and is dependent upon different factors.",
    "In addition, it observed that DT, RF, and XGBoost are the best candidates compared to KNN, SVM, and MLP.",
    "In a tree-based model, all approaches could achieve 100% of test accuracy.",
    "Hence, accounting for the accuracy of the model alone, DT, RF, and XGBoost can be considered as a good preference."
